description.value:
Posh Turkish is an eatery which specializes in authentic Turkish food. We serve healthy food, fast - in a curated and homely setting, hence the name Posh. We know that the art of baking bread and making things like pizza dough from scratch is just a 'tradition' for some. Our lives are getting busier and busier.  We understand that many find it hard make time to prepare and bake real food.  At Posh we are keen to keep traditions and values alive.

Posh offers a large variety of halal meat (lamb, chicken or beef) options from the grill section; kebab, doner and kofte. Patrons are spoilt for choice with a variety of fresh salads to customise their salad or as an accompaniment to their meal.

short_description.value: Eatery specialising in authentic Turkish food

description.value:
Freshly prepared Indian food at your doorstep!
TukTuk is like a short trip to India, full of unique impressions and tasty experiences. TukTuk is inspired by the food hawkers of India, where we do with a mix of rustic roadside and railway station dishes such as dosas and savoury chaats, besides the traditional Indian curries and tandoor dishes. Our food is lovingly prepared and represents the tastes of India today. Rooted in tradition, bursting with aromatic spices and brought to you with a contemporary twist. Gluten controlled, lactose free, vegetarian and vegan options are available. TukTuk uses eco-friendly packaging - our mission is simple, let’s preserve the environment for a better YOU and the PLANET.

short_description.value: From inspiring street food to your favourite Indian curry
